cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.CY 

This paper discusses data poisoning attacks against machine learning models and the use of differential privacy as a defense mechanism. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) as the paper discusses security measures against attacks. The paper also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and data structures (cs.DS) as it discusses different types of learners and algorithms. Finally, the paper involves cyber security (cs.CY) as it discusses attacks and defenses against adversarial manipulation of data.
